name: They Are Behind Me
description:
And I can't run from them, I can't run from myself.

-

Agoraphobic Project, 2022, is an intimate and obsessive series about agoraphobia, depression, obsessive compulsive disorder, bipolar disorder and generalized anxiety disorder. I have been unable to take pictures outside, so this is my agoraphobic inner.


'They Are Behind Me', 2022
